## 🎯 Project Overview

The **Urban Farming Platform** is a comprehensive backend system designed to connect urban dwellers with local farmers, enabling:

- 🌾 **Garden Space Rental** - Rent plots from local farmers
- 🛒 **Organic Marketplace** - Buy and sell fresh organic produce
- 🌱 **Plant Tracking** - Monitor plant growth and health in real-time
- 💬 **Community Forum** - Share gardening tips and eco-friendly practices
- ✅ **Sustainability Certification** - Verified organic products

### 👥 User Roles

| Role         | Permissions                                                            |
| ------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Admin**    | Platform management, user/vendor approval, certification verification  |
| **Vendor**   | Manage farm spaces, list products, track orders, manage certifications |
| **Customer** | Rent spaces, purchase products, track plants, community interaction    |

